source: TEXT_MANFST050_00540_200010_NARRATION<tab>At the Battle of Carteneau, as fire rained down from the heavens...
target:
TEXT_MANFST050_00540_200010_NARRATION<tab>
エオルゼアを震撼させた「カルテノーの戦い」から5年

source: TEXT_MANFST050_00540_200020_NARRATION<tab>Archon Louisoix invoked the power of the Keeper and sent his fellow heroes into an aetherial rift, beyond the reach of the devastation.
target:
TEXT_MANFST050_00540_200020_NARRATION<tab>賢者ルイゾワの秘策により 時を超え
再びエオルゼアの地に降り立った冒険者

source: TEXT_MANFST050_00540_200030_NARRATION<tab>Five years since that fateful day, since the Seventh Umbral Era changed the world forever, the time is come for the heroes to return.
target:
TEXT_MANFST050_00540_200030_NARRATION<tab>その者は今 懐かしの地に足を踏み入れる
第七霊災によって様変わりした その地に

source: TEXT_MANFST050_00540_200040_NARRATION<tab>The Black Shroud─the ancient forest close to the heart of Eorzea.
target:
TEXT_MANFST050_00540_200040_NARRATION<tab>
エオルゼア最大の森林地帯 黒衣森（こくえのもり）

source: TEXT_MANFST050_00540_200050_NARRATION<tab>Beneath the boughs of its towering trees lies the woodland city<var 1F /var>state of Gridania.
target:
TEXT_MANFST050_00540_200050_NARRATION<tab>この地を領する都市国家「グリダニア」は
森の都と謳われる 誉れ高き古都である

source:
TEXT_MANFST050_00540_200060_NARRATION<tab>Once a sanctuary from the world beyond the Hedge, even the mighty elementals, eternal
guardians of the forest, could not forestall the coming of the Seventh Umbral Era.
target:
TEXT_MANFST050_00540_200060_NARRATION<tab>巨大な木造建築物と 無数の水車によって形成された街並みは
黒衣森の樹々に抱かれ 守られているという

source:
TEXT_MANFST050_00540_200070_NARRATION<tab>However, the goddess Nophica was never one to forsake
Her children, and today She welcomes another brave soul...
target:
TEXT_MANFST050_00540_200070_NARRATION<tab>霊災から5年…… 復興に向けて動き出したこの都市に
今ひとりの冒険者が帰ってきた

source: TEXT_MANFST050_00540_200080_NARRATION<tab>...One who shall fight once more to safeguard the future of the realm.
target:
TEXT_MANFST050_00540_200080_NARRATION<tab>
今はまだ 己の運命を知らぬ者……

source:
TEXT_MANFST050_00540_200090_NARRATION<tab>May the Matron take <var 08 E905 ((her)) ((him)) /var> to Her Bosom,
that <var 08 E905 ((she)) ((he)) /var> may never want.
target:
TEXT_MANFST050_00540_200090_NARRATION<tab>
神々に愛されし地 エオルゼアの歴史に名を残す者……

source: TEXT_MANFST050_00540_200100_NARRATION<tab>And in <var 08 E905 ((her)) ((his)) /var> heart sow serenity, purity, and sanctity.
target:
TEXT_MANFST050_00540_200100_NARRATION<tab>この冒険者の長き旅は
森の都グリダニアから 再び始まる
